{{Quote|Shadows cannot live in the dark, Ser Davos. They are servants of light, the children of fire. And the brighter the flame, the darker they are.|[[Melisandre]] to [[Davos Seaworth]]|Garden of Bones}}

A '''Shadowbinder''' is a practitioner of [[magic]] capable of binding shadows to do their will. They seemingly hail from [[Asshai]], one of the easternmost cities of [[the Known World]].
